<paragraph pageId="24" pageNumber="25">Material examined.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="24" pageNumber="25">Holotype ZMUC unnumbered, Fiji Islands, Vitu Levu, Suva Harbour, coll. T. Wolff, 18 May 1965.</paragraph>
